headline.print_headline: Iowa Supreme Court Overturns Conviction in HIV Case
headline.main: Iowa Supreme Court Overturns Conviction in HIV Case

lead_paragraph: The Iowa Supreme Court on Friday set aside the conviction of a man who pleaded guilty to criminal transmission of HIV but later argued that he got insufficient legal advice in making the plea.
